WEBVTT

00:00:04.910 --> 00:00:10.910
Bad news is everywhere.

00:00:10.910 --> 00:00:17.559
You might sometimes wonder if there's any good news.

00:00:17.559 --> 00:00:22.780
The Bible contains good news of something better.

00:00:22.780 --> 00:00:27.899
It can help you to have a happy family life.

00:00:27.899 --> 00:00:32.579
True friendships, inner peace.

00:00:34.380 --> 00:00:37.679
It answers life's big questions such as,

00:00:37.679 --> 00:00:39.979
what is the meaning of life?

00:00:39.979 --> 00:00:42.979
Is God to blame for our suffering?

00:00:42.979 --> 00:00:45.479
What happens when you die?

00:00:45.479 --> 00:00:49.280
Would you like to learn more about the good news?

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:53.979
Read Lesson 1 in the brochure, Good News from God.

00:00:53.979 --> 00:00:57.079
You can download it free of charge from JW.org

00:00:57.079 --> 00:01:00.579
or you can obtain a copy from any of Jehovah's Witnesses.
